  "title": "Lead Software Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>​</strong>Our Client is an established company in Singapore, who is seeking to recruit a Lead Software Engineer.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Advise and guide users from problem definition through to solution design, in both greenfield and brownfield implementations. </li><li>Advise and guide partners from problem definition through to solution design, in both greenfield and brownfield implementations</li><li>Address complex, high-impact challenges at a national scale, driving innovation that improves efficiency and effectiveness across government</li><li>Champion engineering excellence by influencing the adoption and continuous improvement of engineering standards and best practices</li><li>Serve as the lead architect working with industry partner teams to ensure smooth handover from recommendations to implementation—owning the outcomes</li><li>Establish and mentor permanent engineering teams, transferring technical expertise and engineering best practices</li><li>Develop standardised approaches for assessments, discovery, and solution design, and industry best practices</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>10+ years of experience in multi-squad development teams with a career progression to Architect</li><li>Adaptable with experience working in different industries, in-house development and consultancy</li><li>Curious and a problem-solver - understands the need to balance building things right with building the right things</li><li>Actively mentors and cultivates future technical leaders, fostering a culture of continuous learning and excellence</li><li>Exceptional communicator and collaborator - able to communicate effectively with technical and non-technical audiences, with a belief that working across teams and organisations is more effective than operating as a solo unit</li></ul><p>JJ Consulting Services</p><p>EA Licence No.: 12C6207</p><p>Applicants are invited to send in a MS Word resume to <strong>jobs@jjconsulting.com.sg</strong> stating\nposition applying for/present/expected salaries and earliest available date.<br />\n<br />We thank all applicants in advance and regret that only short listed candidates\nwill be notified.</p>",
